thread.title: Eleanor

author: Eleanor
title: Eleanor
text: Great designs to choose from and the editing/customisation process was very easy. Our invitations were printed, shipped and on our doorstep within 3 days. Plus free envelopes! We also took advantage of a half price special which made it incredible value! And the quality of the invitations themselves was great - decent, weighty card and designs exactly as they appeared on screen. Would definitely use again.
